Dunn said he was concerned that "minor problems" in reaching a=20
confidentiality agreement might become a tactic for further delay.=20
The committee gave the six companies until July 10 to reach confidentiality=20
agreements and turn over a vast assortment of records.=20
The contempt finding against Mirant and Enron would be abandoned if they,=20
too, provided the confidential documents by July 10, when the committee will=
=20
review the companies' compliance.=20
The wholesalers also are the targets of similar investigations by Atty. Gen.=
=20
Bill Lockyer and the state Public Utilities Commission.=20
